    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3da55-102">這類成員使用這個列舉型別是<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.FlatStyle%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GroupBox.FlatStyle%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>，和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Label.FlatStyle%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-102">This enumeration is used by members such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.FlatStyle%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GroupBox.FlatStyle%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Label.FlatStyle%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3da55-103">在快顯視窗的 [樣式] 按鈕，這個列舉型別會控制某些行為，以及外觀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-103">In the case of the Popup style button, this enumeration controls some behavior as well as appearance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-104">快顯樣式控制項一開始會顯示一般，直到滑鼠指標移至其上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-104">The Popup style control initially appears Flat until the mouse pointer moves over it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-105">當滑鼠指標移到快顯視窗控制項時，它會顯示為標準的樣式控制項一次將滑鼠指標移它為止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-105">When the mouse pointer moves over the Popup control, it appears as a Standard style control until the mouse pointer is moved off of it again.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3da55-106">如果系統樣式、 控制項的外觀取決於使用者的作業系統，且會忽略下列屬性值： <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BackgroundImage%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>， `ImageAlign`， `Image`， `ImageIndex`， `ImageList`，和`TextAlign`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-106">If the System style is used, the appearance of the control is determined by the user's operating system and the following property values will be ignored: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BackgroundImage%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, `ImageAlign`, `Image`, `ImageIndex`, `ImageList`, and `TextAlign`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-107">颾魤 ㄛ<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BackColor%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>按鈕控制項將會忽略屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-107">In addition, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BackColor%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property will be ignored for button controls.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-108">如果支援，使用者可以變更控制項的外觀，藉由調整其作業系統的外觀設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-108">If supported, users can change the appearance of controls by adjusting the appearance settings of their operating system.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="3da55-109">當<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.FlatStyle%2A>屬性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.RadioButton>並<xref:System.Windows.Forms.CheckBox>類別設為系統、 使用者的作業系統所繪製的控制項和核取對齊根據`CheckAlign`和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.TextAlign%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-109">When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.FlatStyle%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RadioButton> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CheckBox> classes is set to System, the control is drawn by the user's operating system and the check alignment is based upon the `CheckAlign` and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.TextAlign%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-110">`CheckAlign`屬性值未變更，但控制項的外觀可能會受到影響。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-110">The `CheckAlign` property value is not changed, but the appearance of the control can be affected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-111">核取方塊水平對齊控制項 （左或置中對齊會顯示左的對齊，以滑鼠右鍵會保持不變），向左或右邊緣和垂直對齊的描述性文字相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-111">The check box is horizontally aligned with either the left or right edge of the control (a left or center alignment appears left aligned, right remains unchanged), and vertically aligned the same as the descriptive text.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3da55-112">比方說，如果您有<xref:System.Windows.Forms.CheckBox>用來控制`CheckAlign`屬性值<xref:System.Drawing.ContentAlignment?displayProperty=nameWithType>並<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.TextAlign%2A>屬性值<xref:System.Drawing.ContentAlignment?displayProperty=nameWithType>，和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.FlatStyle%2A>屬性值設定為系統中，核取方塊對齊方式將會出現<xref:System.Drawing.ContentAlignment?displayProperty=nameWithType>時的文字對齊方式會維持不變。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-112">For example, if you have a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CheckBox> control with a `CheckAlign` property value of <xref:System.Drawing.ContentAlignment?displayProperty=nameWithType> and a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.TextAlign%2A> property value of <xref:System.Drawing.ContentAlignment?displayProperty=nameWithType>, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ButtonBase.FlatStyle%2A> property value is set to System, the check box alignment will appear to be <xref:System.Drawing.ContentAlignment?displayProperty=nameWithType> while the text alignment remains unchanged.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="3da55-113">設定`FlatStyle`系統的屬性不建議您，如果您需要顯示影像的控制項上顯示某個影像做為控制項的背景，或執行精確的文字對齊方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3da55-113">Setting the `FlatStyle` property to System is not advisable if you need to display an image on a control, display an image as a control's background, or perform precise text alignment.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
